titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: SURFACTANT GIVEN INDICATOR (ON NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE) - Description

div.p: SURFACTANT GIVEN INDICATOR (ON NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE) is the same as attribute SURFACTANT GIVEN INDICATOR, where this takes place on a NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE but not during resuscitation of the PATIENT.
